Package: USgrid
Type: Package
Title: The Demand and Supply for Electricity in the US
Version: 0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Rami", "Krispin", email = "rami.krispin@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Rami Krispin <rami.krispin@gmail.com>
Description: Provides a set of regular time-series datasets, describing the US electricity grid. That includes the total demand and supply, and as well as the demand by energy source (coal, solar, wind, etc.). Source: US Energy Information Administration (Nov 2019).
